啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好灰呀!! 雖然我知一定唔會搵到賺大錢既工。但都想搵份適合自己同有興趣既工</blockquote><br />\n社會就係咁殘酷 魚與熊掌邊有得兼得<br />\n你讀呢啲科預咗就選擇少 而家你有咩條件揀工先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都明白我讀呢科係要預左出路窄。<br />\n而家只係集思廣益，了解下讀中文OR中文教育既人除左教書有冇做緊其他工作，可以比我參考下姐。"},{"pid":"711a03dd1f6fff4e5aeaa4246df830089f2bb9fe","tid":412873,"uid":118334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T05:00:37.000Z","msg":"補習助教？？"},{"pid":"809cccffdcfefa2f6ae320c4fdbf1c12bbeb3573","tid":412873,"uid":61201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T05:01:32.000Z","msg":"HKU?"},{"pid":"b9f883d5cf2489cca2b4b362374f3cde142e1bab","tid":412873,"uid":76432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"出版社"},{"pid":"8dc1b1dd5d72928266989a92dce2c050f5cad23c","tid":412873,"uid":130719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補習助教？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係好想從事教育界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1d6dbb74c32b25b961842613a748d1995ce4c1","tid":412873,"uid":130719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出版社</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我都係諗緊呢條路，不過見到好多相關POST話要識人介紹，好難入行。唔知係咪真。<br />\n<br />\n有冇行內既巴絲可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975465303ee50bd352b459e1b2010a2b946dcfa7","tid":412873,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T05:41:23.000Z","msg":"小說家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59faad42fe7578a0b965dfc3859000d838ebd29","tid":412873,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"m記"},{"pid":"