te>教科書編輯<br />\n媒體編輯<br />\nCopywriter</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係對編輯有興趣，巴打係咪行內人?可否講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n準備轉做地盤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打本身係出版社編輯?"},{"pid":"66e07e0cc3e0f955d826377ce7fd907ae4e92cbb","tid":412873,"uid":139114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好灰呀!! 雖然我知一定唔會搵到賺大錢既工。但都想搵份適合自己同有興趣既工</blockquote><br />\n社會就係咁殘酷 魚與熊掌邊有得兼得<br />\n你讀呢啲科預咗就選擇少 而家你有咩條件揀工先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都明白我讀呢科係要預左出路窄。<br />\n而家只係集思廣益，了解下讀中文OR中文教育既人除左教書有冇做緊其他工作，可以比我參考下姐。</blockquote><br />\n盡量唔好做呢科既「出路」,出版，補習人工太低冇乜前途，除非你真心有興趣唔介意<br />\n唔好抗拒入商業機構，太多文科撚唔敢做商業機構寧願做大學文員，幾年後仲搵萬頭先嚟後悔"},{"pid":"a972a38c470c10bc23294c65a3ca9031d36cfcdc","tid":412873,"uid":128220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年FINAL YEAR，好清楚自己唔係教書既料。<br />\n<br />\n其實比較想從事文字工作，少D對人既工    E.G 編輯 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，仲有冇其他出路?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跪求</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教書都未必搵到啦老友<br />\n<br />\n利伸：教過中學四年，已轉行"},{"pid":"26bfc63f9e867da51d0f181910285048f577a08a","tid":412873,"uid":46649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>教科書編輯<br />\n媒體編輯<br />\nCopywriter</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係對編輯有興趣，巴打係咪行內人?可否講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n準備轉做地盤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打本身係出版社編輯?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，人工會跑輸大市。"},{"pid":"5d0692a89daef26526fc0b78d628c3e18fd4e783","tid":412873,"uid":130719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好灰呀!! 雖然我知一定唔會搵到賺大錢既工。但都想搵份適合自己同有興趣既工</blockquote><br />\n社會就係咁殘酷 魚與熊掌邊有得兼得<br />\n你讀呢啲科預咗就選擇少 而家你有咩條件揀工先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都明白我讀呢科係要預左出路窄。<br />\n而家只係集思廣益，了解下讀中文OR中文教育既人除左教書有冇做緊其他工作，可以比我參考下姐。</blockquote><br />\n盡量唔好做呢科既「出路」,出版，補習人工太低冇乜前途，除非你真心有興趣唔介意<br />\n唔好抗拒入商業機構，太多文科撚唔敢做商業機構寧願做大學文員，幾年後仲搵萬頭先嚟後悔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打講得幾有道理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身為文科撚真係有d抗拒做商業機構。<br />\n或者我都應該考慮下呢個方向，多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed56b20ca9bda84f79d7acbcba872dd498d8718","tid":412873,"uid":130719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>教科書編輯<br />\n媒體編輯<br />\nCopywriter</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係對編輯有興趣，巴打係咪行內人?可否講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n準備轉做地盤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打本身係出版社編輯?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，人工會跑輸大市。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣我都好明白。但我都好有興趣想知工作量係咪好大？經常通宵？一開頭做助理編輯會做d咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67addad313f9032f7089d8929c601eefb6ed2feb","tid":412873,"uid":139114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm