=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝，其實一黎個人意願唔想做，二黎係因為大學有一個老師點醒我，內容大概就係你冇教師個份熱誠既話，就不如唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(唔原文quote，驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</span></span>"},{"pid":"3c0e9ad72615e8d21a56f8ddb872283f48c73210","tid":412873,"uid":130719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"不可以沉下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac057d490365428bdc3037f12243cc93d05800f4","tid":412873,"uid":86774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:47:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不可以沉下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你屋企有冇負擔？"},{"pid":"b62b3c4d8872aca929ccf7ae1b68d3d75cfc16f0","tid":412873,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:57:54.000Z","msg":"17中文系畢業<br />\n仲做緊雙失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e4d030beab07b2ea551016fa56a2af314076da","tid":412873,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:59:51.000Z","msg":"英文教育唔讀，讀科垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0e222b0339e1e16526f67e0768593ce90a074e","tid":412873,"uid":2766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:03:57.000Z","msg":"唔想誤人子弟<br />\n當初讀咩中文教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1bd25919c6399fe4cecf47ebf3343c81ef3e46","tid":412873,"uid":81762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:23:48.000Z","msg":"Copywriter /editor好多要求要有portfolio <br />\n你不妨搵下pt黎做<br />\n草下經驗先"},{"pid":"93ce73f6dfd7242790a79c1f3f7c75508f5feef0","tid":412873,"uid":53441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:54:15.000Z","msg":"英文系留名<img src